title: DAO Academy & Sarcophagus DAO December Partnership Renewal
body:
This is a revote due to the previous vote not reaching quorum.

DAO Academy & Sarcophagus DAO Partnership Proposal
This vote is for an agreed partnership between DAO
Academy, and the Sarcophagus DAO community. This Partnership will enlist
the administrative services of DAO Academy for the growth and proliferation of
the Sarcophagus DAO, and administration of the community centric programs
and activities listed
